Monthly CELO Distributions: Starting May 2025, 10,000 CELO is distributed monthly across three tiers:Tier 1: Top 10 builders share 50% of the reward pool, proportional to their activity and impact.
Tier 2: Next 25 builders share 25% of the pool.
Tier 3: Next 65 builders share the remaining 25%.

Evaluation Criteria: Rankings are based on:Activity on verified Celo contracts during the month.
Contributions to public crypto repositories.
Builder Score on the day of calculation.

